result.name: Victoria Harbour Restaurant

reviews.text: The food is acceptable and the seating space is narrow.

The food was OK, little to salty for my taste. Their bean paste buns and roasted piglets are very good. But over all its like well kept restaurants. What I didn't like was the service and not fresh seafood. When we went to eat a pre-order set, the waitress insisted that the promotion was over. After we explained that we've order it two days ago, she still insisted that it was over. The dispute was settle after we found the promotion paper sitting on the next table clearly stating another before the promotion was over. For compensation they did comp the dessert and the fruit.
Typical HK tea house, not much special but dim sum are fine.
Food is acceptable and the price is reasonable.
Good food and great for families

result.name: 海港酒家

reviews.text:
真的經常去茶樓飲茶呢~ 這次又去飲茶了
這家在我家附近 已經好一段時間沒食

那次去到是中午時間 要等一陣子位才行
現在只剩下拼桌坐了 不過以等其他🙄🙄

·黑金流沙包 HKD$18.8
·鮑汁鳳爪 HKD$16.8
·咸菜豬肚 HKD$23.8
·相思豆小白兔 HKD$18
·五香咸水角 HKD$16

味道也與之前食的一樣味道 不過不失
可惜的是服務態度大不如前 有點失望[流泪]
這是一間傳統中式點心酒家，環境都不錯，飲茶要搭檯，食物都算不錯，勝在夠熱。職員招呼一般，可能太忙吧，所以很多時態度較差。
食品真係得，比其他分店好食!
集團式酒樓算是不錯、服務態度良好、出品中上水準、在天水圍都算旺場、要訂位！
最正係燒鵝，冇得頂，食物好食，但出餐太慢
